page.title: 19A TYPICAL DAY - JONATHAN
page.content: I get up at 6.30am,have breakfast at at 7.00am.I walk to school at 8.45am. When we reach school we go into the classroom and do some sums on the blackboard.We go into hymn pratice and sing lots of songs.Afterwards we go back to class and do some work.At 10.30 we go out to play.If it is on the field I guard the trees and if not I play on the playground.We come in at 10.45am and do some more work.At 11.55am we clear away and have some of a story.At 12.00noon I walk home and have some lunch.I have a play and then go back at 1.25pm.Then I do some work then go out to play.We come in at 2.45pm and do some more work. .At 3.30pm we go home and go to Boys Brigade at 6.00pm,and play lots of games.At 7.30pm we go home and go to bed.
